YIUVSCvTFW2oef2h3tg">Trư Sơn Nguyễn thị từ - 豬山阮氏祠</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Th%E1%BA%A3n/author-Rf5MQH5zACpwcSwDnHFWvQ">Lý Trần Thản</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/Tuy%E1%BB%81n-thu%E1%BB%B7-3/poem-63sQ6igz79c8AB4tN4pK2g">Tuyền thuỷ 3 - 泉水 3</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/U-nh%C3%A2n/poem-Dpws_IYIm_LPKzeJTUNyTA">U nhân - 幽人</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/U%E1%BB%95ng-ng%C6%B0ng-my/poem-LwjlQcYSe68hDMDugKb1Kg">Uổng ngưng my - 枉凝眉</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/author-1DK3jrzNRQ6A5gusK7iSPw">Tào Tuyết Cần</a>)<br></div>	</div>
